                    <h4 class="cd-text cd-title">feature panel</h4>
                    <p class="cd-text">Use a feature panel where you want the content to stand out. For example, to draw attention to an important
                        section in a longer list of content.</p>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-xs-4">
                            <div class="panel panel--feature">
    <div class="panel__header">
        <h2>panel header</h2>
    </div>
